Package org.mule.context

Class Summary
DefaultMuleContextBuilder Implementation of MuleContextBuilder that uses DefaultMuleContext as the default MuleContext implementation and builds it with defaults values for MuleConfiguration, LifecycleManager, WorkManager, WorkListener and ServerNotificationManager.
DefaultMuleContextFactory Default implementation that stores MuleContext in MuleServer static and uses DefaultMuleContextBuilder to build new MuleContext instances.
